ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course provides an overview of Cartularies, Charters, and Archives with specific examples of these materials. Access to Beinecke materials was indespensible to a thorough understanding of the materials as they once existed and were utilized. I would and have recommended this course.
I would recommend this course for any student seeking a greater understanding of the mateials available as sources for Medievalists.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course illuminated an aspect of Medieval History that I had never considered previously. The knowledge I gained will be very useful to my continuing projects.
